snippet.title: Is WB Planning to Fire Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 If Need Be?
snippet.description:
Is WB Planning to Fire Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 If Need Be?

Scooper Grace Randolph claims that WB's filming Aquaman 2 in a way where they can cut Amber Heard's Mera from the movie if they need to. Basically, if her image takes a hit from bad press generated from news about her court cases with Johnny Depp, they want to be able to decrease her screen time. Same with Johnny Depp regarding Fantastic Beasts 3. 

I discuss in this video, so check it out.
